        <li>Mirror delamination or separation of the reflective coating not caused by external damage</li>
        <li>Abnormal rust or corrosion of stainless steel components under normal indoor conditions</li>
        <li>Defects in materials or workmanship present at the time of manufacture</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section reveal">
      <h2>What's Not Covered</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Accidental damage, impact, or breakage</li>
        <li>Damage caused by improper installation or failure to follow care instructions</li>
        <li>Normal wear and minor surface marks consistent with everyday use</li>
        <li>Damage caused by exposure to outdoor conditions, excessive humidity, or direct water contact</li>
        <li>Cosmetic damage that does not affect the function of the product</li>
      </ul>
