        <div class="warranty-step"><span class="warranty-step-num">02</span><div class="warranty-step-body"><h4>Assessment</h4><p>Our team will review your claim within 3–5 working days and confirm whether it falls within the warranty terms.</p></div></div>
        <div class="warranty-step"><span class="warranty-step-num">03</span><div class="warranty-step-body"><h4>Resolution</h4><p>Where a valid claim is confirmed, we will arrange a repair, replacement, or — where neither is possible — a full refund of the original purchase price.</p></div></div>
